Name: Cube Crisis
About the game: Cube Crisis, a casual single-player game that tests hand-eye coordination, needs SUPER control ability to avoid blocks which are moving faster and faster. The game provides 4 different levels of difficulty. Press the button you set to avoid the blocks. You may either choose to play in the Scene or break records through competitive missions!
